@startuml UC_27_Assign_Roles
title UC-27: Assign Roles

|User|
start
:(1) Open the role management panel;
:(2) Invite a member as moderator;
:(3) Submit the role assignment;

|System|
:(4) Validate creator permissions;
:(5) Add the moderator invitation record;
:(6) Notify or activate the role for the target user;
:(7) Return the updated role list;

stop
@enduml
